        on {{ event.start_date }}</h1>
    <p>Start: {{ event.start }}<br/>Finish: {{ event.finish }}</p>
    <div class="badge">
        <img alt="Volunteer status"
             src="/{{ series.slug }}/{{ event.id }}/status.svg">
    </div>
    <p>Wee need at least {{ event.volunteers_goal }} volunteers. Currently
        {{ event.volunteers_current }} have joined.</p>
